content: Hi can one of the staff connect me with the link to sign up for text bank? I had asked in the general chat yesterday and was given the link but I can’t find it now. TIA ☺️

Hi <@779382569534881824> here is the link https://discord.com/channels/1242249109298221066/1266829704204386334 once you are onboarded you will see text campaigns sent out during the day. You participate in campaigns whenever you can.
